Subject: drm/lima: Convert to platform remove callback returning void
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 980ec6444372db785b2ca86e18df155bc7e664ed
